title: Parallel Lives 2: Maegor the Cruel & Gregor Clegane
description:
The second installment of Parallel Lives: Maegor Targaryen and Gregor Clegane. Stay tuned until the end for the preview of the next pairing, and let us know your guess for the next two characters. (This one's a bit better if watched, but perfectly cromulent as audio-only).
